Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果姐姐隐瞒了什么 你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,比如在甲州胜沼时 明明援军不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,却必须命令战斗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,近藤勇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么突然说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我会跟随你的 无论发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因为姐姐是唯一的家人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,把黑板上的三句话分别分节试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.34,NoticeB,,0,0,0,,{\frz-16\pos(959.785,646.285)}咖喱喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.34,NoticeB,,0,0,0,,{\frz-45\pos(564,837)}吃我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,比较像勇者部的文化祭节目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:08:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,结城同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是没什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那能请你读出现在讲到的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,手机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,上课时请切断电源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡同学也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对不起 停下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧 不是吧 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,树！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 大家都怪怪的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,树
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,树 好好听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们中了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 姐姐~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这是… 发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这一天 我们的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时 结束了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,明明刚才还在教室里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我又睡着了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,疼 似乎不是在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 电话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,画面变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,风前辈 小树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,总算找到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,风前辈 小树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你们两个都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不幸中的万幸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个要是没有拿着手机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这个app还有这种功能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,隐藏功能？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这个隐藏功能是产生这种情况时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,自动启动的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 好方便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这个app 是入部时风前辈让下载的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,风前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,大家冷静下来听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是大赦派来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 大赦是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,供奉神树大人的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么特别任务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,明明一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事我还是第一次听说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没中 我是打算就这样瞒过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,风前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我的班 赞州中学勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,中了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,现在看到的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是神树大人造出的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,神树大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那么… 不是什么坏的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 但是 被神树大人选中的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,必须在这里面和敌人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,什么战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这个点是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,幸亏是个慢速的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,浮在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs29.997\bord2.997\pos(1023,982.503)}Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那是宿命点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了杀死世界而攻过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,人类的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,杀死世界是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,宿命点的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,到达世界的恩惠 神树大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候 世界就会死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界里 只有我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 是我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,通过大赦的调查 你们被判断为最有资质
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:13.78,Notice,,0,0,0,,全市乡镇中学 勇者资质报告书 机密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会… 怎么可能和那种东西战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,办法是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,只要表现出战斗的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这个app的功能就会解锁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,从而成为神树大人的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,盯上我们了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,已经发现我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗什么的 不可能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,带上东乡逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,树也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么能扔下姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,树…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我会跟随你的 无论发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好 树 跟我上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,树 着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是被神树大人选中的勇者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是守护这个世界的精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,通过神树大人的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:18:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,会把力量借给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,树 闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,坐过山车啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,把手扬起来 表现出战斗的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎… 出来了什么武器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,风前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 连上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,风前辈 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,现在在战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,比起担心我 你那边没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,数量太多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 东乡 抱歉瞒着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,风前辈是为大家着想才没说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一直一个人没法挑明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是正符合勇者部的活动目的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不是风前辈的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈 小树！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 不要管我 你快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么话 怎么能把朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,扔下朋友不管什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:20:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事我绝对做不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里舍弃朋友的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是勇者！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.84,0:21:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有人受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,留下痛苦的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为了不让大家留下那种回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我要努力！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:21:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:21:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.65,0:22:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.01,0:22:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.02,0:22:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是踊跃地助人为乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我是赞州中学勇者部 结城友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.47,0:22:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我要成为勇者！
